sequenceDiagram
    participant UA as User A (Sender)
    participant CB as ChatBubble
    participant SC as Socket Client
    participant SS as Socket Server
    participant API as REST API
    participant DB as Database
    participant UB as User B (Receiver)

    Note over UA,UB: Message Sending Flow
    
    UA->>CB: Types message & clicks send
    CB->>CB: Validates input
    CB->>SC: Emits 'send_message' event
    
    SC->>SS: WebSocket emission
    SS->>API: POST /api/chat/messages
    API->>DB: Save message
    DB-->>API: Message saved
    API-->>SS: Return message object
    
    SS->>SC: Broadcast 'new_message'
    SC->>CB: Update message list
    CB->>UA: Display message (optimistic)
    
    SS->>UB: Forward 'new_message'
    UB->>UB: Display message
    
    Note over UA,UB: Read Receipt Flow
    
    UB->>CB: Opens conversation
    CB->>SC: Emit 'message_read'
    SC->>SS: Forward read receipt
    SS->>UA: Notify message read
    UA->>UA: Update status to 'read'
